attribute.description:
PROC_CHIP Attribute Binary vector where the most significant bits (0:11) identify the delay to be used for that step of the sequence. Power up goes from 11, then 10, then 9,.... then 0.
0 in the bit position: use ATTR_PM_PFET_POWERUP_CORE_DELAY0;
1 in the bit position: use ATTR_PM_PFET_POWERUP_CORE_DELAY1

